          <div style="margin-left: 0px; position: relative; width: 700px; z-index: 5; " id="body_layer">
            <div style="height: 0px; line-height: 0px; " class="bumper"> </div>
            <div style="height: 1px; line-height: 1px; " class="tinyText"> </div>
            <div style="margin-left: 222px; margin-top: 326px; position: relative; width: 448px; z-index: 1; " class="style_SkipStroke_1 shape-with-text flowDefining">
              <div class="text-content style_External_448_320" style="padding: 0px; ">
                <div class="style">
                  <p style="padding-top: 0pt; " class="paragraph_style">Databases<br /></p>
                  <p class="paragraph_style_1"><a class="class1" href="http://splicer.unibe.ch/cgi-bin/gbrowse/Tbrucei_chr1/" title="http://splicer.unibe.ch/cgi-bin/gbrowse/Tbrucei_chr1/"><span style="line-height: 28px; " class="style_1">SLT</span></a> (spliced leader trapping)<br /></p>
                  <p class="paragraph_style_1">Here you find expression profiling and splicing data corresponding to the recently accepted manuscript “<span class="style_2">Spliced leader trapping reveals widespread alternative splicing patterns in the highly dynamic transcriptome of Trypanosoma brucei</span>” by Nilson <span class="style_2">et al.</span>. <br /></p>
                  <p class="paragraph_style_1">We use this database for our expression/splicing analysis. The data found in the SLT database can also be accessed through the much better curated and much more comprehensive <a title="http://tritrypdb.org/tritrypdb/" class="class2" onkeypress="window.open(this.href); return false;" onclick="window.open(this.href); return false;" href="http://tritrypdb.org/tritrypdb/">TriTryp</a> database and <a title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo/" class="class3" onkeypress="window.open(this.href); return false;" onclick="window.open(this.href); return false;" href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo/">GEO</a>.<br /></p>
                  <p class="paragraph_style_1"><br /></p>
                  <p class="paragraph_style_1"><a title="http://splicer.unibe.ch/kiss/" onkeypress="window.open(this.href); return false;" onclick="window.open(this.href); return false;" href="http://splicer.unibe.ch/kiss/" style="line-height: 28px; " class="style_1">KISS</a><span style="line-height: 28px; " class="style_3"> </span>(Kinetoplast RNA editing sequence search tool)<br /></p>
                  <p style="padding-bottom: 0pt; " class="paragraph_style_1">Is a workbench for the analysis of RNA editing and a well annotated set of gRNAs for <span class="style_2">T. brucei</span> (<a title="http://www.izb.unibe.ch/res/ochsenreiter/PDF/Ochsenreiter 2006 RNA-1.pdf" class="class4" onkeypress="window.open(this.href); return false;" onclick="window.open(this.href); return false;" href="http://www.izb.unibe.ch/res/ochsenreiter/PDF/Ochsenreiter%202006%20RNA-1.pdf">Ochsenreiter <span class="style_2">et al.</span> 2006</a>)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            


